case.name: Martin v State of Western Australia (Corrigendum dated 13 November 2008) [2008] FCA 1677 (12 November 2008)

citances.sentence: There is little doubt that the proposed amendments to the claimant application are designed to facilitate the registration of the claimant application under s 190C of the Act. As to the history of registration of the claimant application in this proceeding, see Martin v State of Western Australia [2008] FCA 1677.
